<P>
 TWELVE RED HERRINGS by Jeffrey Archer (HarperCollins: $23). Welcome to virtual 
reading. The "facts," as Archer serves them up here, are not always what they 
seem.These 12 novellas take some unexpected twist and turns; in one, you get to 
pick your own ending. (Also available on audiocassette.) 
