"Stormy" O'Donnell travels to Atlanta to write for the local magazine and find 
love. Veering away from her standard format, Anne Rivers Siddons introduces the 
combustible element of the 1960s civil-rights movement into this romance. (Also 
available on audiocassette.) 
</P>
