<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE POLITICS OF INCLUSION FOR WOMEN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * I read with tired amusement Eileen Padberg's latest rantings that "women" 
are excluded from Orange County politics by a male chauvinist conspiracy headed 
by the chief hobgoblin in Padberg's demonology, (Orange County Republican 
Central Committee Chairman) Tom Fuentes. What nonsense! If Padberg bothered to 
read the Republican Party of Orange County Central Committee's roster of 
members, she'd discover that not only are the majority of them women, but that 
the first vice chairman is also a woman (Dr. Jo Ellen Allen, and the county 
