<HEADLINE>
<P>
MAY DUNKENTALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * Too bad it took a drive-by shooting to find out about the Watts matriarch 
May Dunkentall (July 2).Why don't we read about such colorful community figures 
before they die? I live in a "good area," Playa del Rey, yet no one cooks soul 
food for the neighborhood.  
</P>
<P>
 Dunkentall did more for Watts than all the city politicians and bureaucrats 
combined. She showed she cared, she created community. More articles about 
people like her, community heroes, would encourage more people to follow her 
role model. 
</P>
<P>
 I'd like to see an article about a community hero on the front page every day. 
</P>
<P>
 DAVID QUESTON 
</P>
<P>
 Santa Monica 
</P>
</TEXT>
