<TEXT>
<P>
 An 80-year-old Ventura woman was killed in a head-on collision on California 
118 near Grimes Canyon Road early Saturday morning when her car crossed over 
the double yellow line and struck a tractor-trailer, the California Highway 
Patrol said. 
</P>
<P>
