 Late Saturday, police identified the girl as 2-year-old Karen Nguyen. 
</P>
<P>
 Lewis said the accident occurred at 7:52 p.m. on 15th Street, between Monroe 
Lane and Newland Street, in an area that includes numerous apartments. Police 
had few leads Saturday night and appealed to the public for information that 
might assist investigators in apprehending the driver and locating the vehicle. 
</P>
