<DOCID> 059433 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
July 10, 1994, Sunday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4 
